        "en": "1.\tBuilding Reading Skills &amp; Exploring Interests in Reading.<br>2.\tImproving Logical Reason Skills<br>3.\tThe Expression of Language &amp; Writing  <br>4.\tExploring Its Life Philosophy behind the works. <br>5.\tEnhancing Abilities of Listening, Speaking, Reading &amp; Writing.<br>"
